# Update Documentation Before Opening PRs

Before creating a pull request, check whether the changes affect anything documented in:

1. **`tasks/prd-wow-profession-recipes.md`** — the data model, functional requirements, or technical considerations
2. **`README.md`** — the project structure, recipe JSON schema, setup instructions, or deployment steps

If the PR introduces new fields, changes the database schema, modifies the recipe JSON format, adds new scripts/commands, or alters the project structure, update the relevant docs in the same PR.
